<cl=A2A2A2>
The guild of Assassins is the most mysterious and secret of all guilds in Sphere. They don't pay much attention to the magic of elements and to endurance training here, but the dexterity of Assassins has become legendary. Their mysterious ability to be invisible makes an assassin an extremely dangerous enemy. Assassins know for sure where to strike to cause maximum damage to the enemy. Besides, they are generally recognized as experts in poisons.
<br><br>
